summary: My ENB configuration,That aims on performance, but keep vanilla taste
descriptionHtml:
This ENB preset is for mid range pc or for people that don\'t want a high
FPS drop...
.
.
.
.
.
You can enhance the image with imaginator
Preset 9 and 4 make a nice combination
.
.
.
.
.
I have no problem if you tweak this and reupload this anywhere else
.
.
.
.
.
FPS drop is very small 2 - 4 with Performance option depends on your
system ;-)
.
.
.
.
After a few tweaks with this ENB HiAlgo started being incompatible and
don\'t know what is causing it srry HiAlgo users :/
.
.
.
.
Instalation:
All you need to do is pick one of the ENB (Performance,Quality+Performance,
Quality) open it and put all the files in your Skyrim Main folder....
There is a few Optionals So tweak with them as you like ;-)
.
.
.
I am new to ENB and modding so i am ready for feedback ;-)
.
.
.
People that like very sharp ENB shouldn\'t use this one cause it\'s not the very sharp
Hope my english isn\'t taht bad :P
.
.
.
.
